                              'HipBarr' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'HipBarr' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move a coloured
diagonal bar that spans two tiles, so it gets to the exit tile. To
complicate matters a little, there are other bars that are placed
here and there which may be in the way, so you have to move those
bars so the coloured bar can get to the exit tile.

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves...

  Have fun!

